title: S_OP == && M_OP >= || M_OP >= && S_OP like
query: In courses dataset courses, find entries whose Department is "cnps" and Average is greater than 89.060001 or Pass is not less than 13.001 and Instructor includes ", alanaise"; show Department and ID, Instructor, Title, UUID, Average, Pass, Fail and Audit; sort in ascending order by Department, ID, Average and Pass.
